response.overview: Recorded live at the Summer Breeze Open Air Festival of 2002, and released initially as a bonus DVD along with German metal band Brainstorm's fifth album, "Soul Temptation".  Setlist: "Metus Mortis (Intro)", "Blind Suffering", "Crush Depth", "Shadowland", "Voices", "Checkmate In Red", "Liar's Edge", "Hollow Hideaway", "Under Lights"
response.title: Brainstorm : Live Suffering
